  <title translate="true">Root Depth Pane</title>
  <body>
    <header>
      <para styleclass="Heading1"><text styleclass="Heading1" translate="true">Root Depth Pane</text></para>
    </header>
    <para styleclass="Normal"><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true">This pane is on the </text><link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="Farm_Crop_Properties_Dialog_Bo" styleclass="Strong" translate="true">Farm Land Use Properties</link><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true"> dialog box.</text></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true">The root depth is distance from the land surface to the bottom of the root zone. The root depth must be greater than zero unless </text><link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="Groundwater-Root-Interaction-P" styleclass="Normal" translate="true">GROUNDWATER_ROOT_INTERACTION</link><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true"> = 0 or 1 (no transpiration or no groundwater root interaction).</text></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"></para>
  </body>
